0aj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2XOf0aj&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0NVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=2294a012\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2XOf0aj</a><br />\n隨時 - 捐款民調 - <a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/donation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fdonation&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0NVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=a33e730e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/donation</a><br />\n隨時 - 「反送中」民情報告眾籌計劃<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/854\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F854&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0NVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=14c77da4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/854</a><br />\n隨時 - 連儂牆"},{"pid":"ba2cf167b9d565e700c1b1345bcaca35ca62624b","tid":1308013,"uid":90595,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:34:43.000Z","msg":"我細個會 但而家大個左就唔會<br />\n有時唔係好明d人出左社會仲成日咁嘅心態有咩謂<br />\n其實每個人都平等 何必同人比呢<br />\n你唔會因為著件名牌就會好睇左<br />\n其實你著左我都唔識分 識分都唔會care<br />\n喺唔同家庭環境下鬥搵多錢更加冇意義<br />\n極其量搵個初始條件同你差唔多嘅 搵對方做reference從而提升自己對個社會嘅貢獻仲好<br />\n呢個城市太多人look for money﹐太少人look for values<br />\n即使你做到社會top 1% 呢個世界仍然有幾千萬人勁過你"},{"pid":"d9b562fccc10a5117e0a85a4ff9021df7d2bda6a","tid":1308013,"uid":4811,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:40:20.000Z","msg":"想開心啲，只要你選擇生活、交往嘅都係比自己差或廢嘅圈子，你都會快樂好多，不過從細到大都知要進步就要結交比自己優越嘅人，但代價就係活喺你所講嘅世界度，講到尾都係點樣攞平衡"},{"pid":"850547597cf07b87871d9c49c8a9d1f9b8ba221a","tid":1308013,"uid":89200,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:43:40.000Z","msg":"每個人價值觀唔同 如果生存左幾十年 個人仲on99 走去用社會普遍價值觀去衡量自己成就 未免太可憐"},{"pid":"4a4ba95db6a4d19b2fce9de6c16aa636646b03f4","tid":1308013,"uid":254388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:46:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7670fac40ed64609822cfb616678762af71689f3","tid":1308013,"uid":174530,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:47:44.000Z","msg":"我有錢靚仔有事業有學識，最鍾意同人比較<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb2b2e35677619a55ad2cda9d0ddb4927988ecf","tid":1308013,"uid":95097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:57:52.000Z","msg":"其實唔比較會幸福好多 做好自己就得<br />\n贏同輸都係睇邊個係對象 一日未到最後都唔知"},{"pid":"7cb797a79117271e1813c06797c12315641356c1","tid":1308013,"uid":49004,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:59:43.000Z","msg":"啲聰明撚讀乜科都勁 就算隊本可蘭經比佢讀 佢一樣可以考到第一<br />\n自己就算有興趣的科目 讀3,4粒鐘都唔熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7281d846c31d50878387daeb76c3902e8470e8ed","tid":1308013,"uid":51735,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:07:54.000Z","msg":"中撚到癲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e11c35289c1f5c54e8d48868ea2d38510ab18b","tid":1308013,"uid":8290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cb797a79117271e1813c06797c12315641356c1","tid":1308013,"uid":49004,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:59:43.000Z","msg":"啲聰明撚讀乜科都勁 就算隊本可蘭經比佢讀 佢一樣可以考到第一<br />\n自己就算有興趣的科目 讀3,4粒鐘都唔熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:45:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7982b6738097c4bb1dc68ec826563c5b4a77d068","tid":1308013,"uid":8290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:40:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"063cad64060bf940fdc89207b2739004ce786860","tid":1308013,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T04:41:08.000Z","msg":"我做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"